Waves
=====

This project bundles a WebGL FFT ocean simulation (`simulation.js`, `shared.js`,
`waves.js`) derived from publicly circulated WebGL ocean demos that implement
Stockham FFT spectrum updates on the GPU.

Buoy integration, PHP proxying, layout consolidation, and station polling were
added for pinchards.is/waves.

